{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/sapientnitro/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"3b20eaf3-083d-5377-97d6-a62d048ce31d","html":"<p>As part of my work as a senior interactive developer at SapientNitro, I started to architect and build an internal application to manage the technical skills of Sapient developers across the world.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.199999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/d1f95/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/dbdff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I got two other developers on board (for a couple of weeks) and we started to work on it. The app was built using Sails.js, an MVC framework based on Express/Node.js that creates a REST API with the endpoints defined by the models. We also connected to the Active Directory to fetch employee data and used Sapient’s user credentials to sign-up and sign-in users.</p>\n<p>The DB was driven by Mongo (we used Mongolabs for testing) and for the UI we used Bootstrap. The app allows admins to create/edit/delete new skils and categories.</p>\n<p>Developers can update their skills (using a level criteria) and managers can review them and also assign a value to them.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1252px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d7bd275ce2d7ec66bd498d35c791034f/af4d4/0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"0\"\n        title=\"0\"\n        src=\"/static/d7bd275ce2d7ec66bd498d35c791034f/af4d4/0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d7bd275ce2d7ec66bd498d35c791034f/d1f95/0.jpg 500w,\n/static/d7bd275ce2d7ec66bd498d35c791034f/dbdff/0.jpg 1000w,\n/static/d7bd275ce2d7ec66bd498d35c791034f/af4d4/0.jpg 1252w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1248px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6211b36ae6088aa7a1a40d2226bb4bf4/1e841/6.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        